{
  "stem": "1736.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A few of my friends who managed to put their age up, managed to join the Jewish Brigade, and then go back to fight the Germans with the Jewish brigade and liberate--",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish Brigade was a brigade of Palestinian Jewish citizens.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm using Palestinian here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Israeli, because Israel was not in existence then-- formed as part of I think the 8th Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were sent back there to fight, you know, and liberate Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were able to help out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they worked with translators and liberate camps and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't able to get my age up for them to believe me to do that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that's what everybody wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everybody--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--would want to do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But on the other hand, there were other things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, you know-- there were many things that had to be done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because during that time, this was a time when the immigrant ships were arriving.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the meantime, the Haganah had been formed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, as members of the kibbutz and young members, we became part of the Haganah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were trained at the time with guns and all the things that go with it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Also, in readiness for the creation of the state, which would come eventually, there was the Palmach, you know, that when they are doing things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there's all sorts of stories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I'd need another 10 tapes to tell you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the elite group of the Haganah, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] captions of--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were the Red Berets, if you like, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're doing special jobs of blowing up bridges, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] anything that needs to be done, which is the commanders.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
